              .item__main-box__right__column-right__box__link-text ナイキ
          %td#item__main-box__right__column-right__state.item__main-box__right__column-right__box
            新品、未使用
          %td#item__main-box__right__column-right__burden.item__main-box__right__column-right__box
            送料込み(出品者負担)
